FBIS4-37075 "drnes116_v_94002" FBIS-NES-94-116 Daily Report 15 Jun 1994 Pakistan Islamabad Carefully Watching U.S-DPRK `Standoff' Islamabad Carefully Watching U.S-DPRK `Standoff' BK1506143894 Islamabad PTV Television Network in English 1400 GMT 15 Jun 94 BK1506143894 Islamabad PTV Television Network English BFN [Text] In Islamabad, a Foreign Office spokesman, while replying to a question on U.S.-North Korea standoff, told newsmen that Pakistan as a member of the UN Security Council is watching the situation carefully. Pakistan, he said, has always upheld the sanctity of international agreements, but at the same time it emphasized that sovereignty of nations and dignity of states must always be an important factor in international diplomacy.
